description: Welcome to Unit 503 at The Ellery!  A 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom gem in the heart of Southie's most exciting neighborhood with sweeping city views! This spacious abode boasts a generous 660 sq feet of living space. Step inside to discover the perfect retreat, complete with a private deck and a great layout that's both functional and stylish. The wide plank oak flooring and Calcutta quartz counters exude elegance, while the oversized cabinets and custom closets offer ample storage. With in-unit laundry, convenience is at your fingertips. But that's not all – this home is transit-oriented and located close to major highways, offering easy access to the city and beyond. Plus, the common terrace and kitchenette provide a great space to entertain and unwind. Situated in a prime location, this property is ripe for appreciation, making it an excellent investment opportunity. Whether you're a savvy investor or a discerning homeowner, this home is ready to fulfill your urban living dreams.
